title.rendered: Gunther. FW 2023/2024 during Paris Fashion Week

content.rendered:
Gunther. Collection Autumn & Winter 2023/2024

GUNTHER is a men's fashion brand founded in Paris by Naomi Gunther and Gabin Ducourant. Graduate of the Parsons School of Design in New York City, Naomi Gunther questions very early on the codes of men's fashion through audacious collections and a strong attention to detail. Particularly sensitive to textures, the designer defends a style that is effortlessly chic in all circumstances, timeless and remarkable. Made in France, crafted in Parisian workshops, GUNTHER showcases French know-how and advocates for a responsible and ethical fashion.


Text and Photo: Press Gunther

Thanks: Dresscode

More on: www.guntherparis.com @guntherparis


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
